Interface DuplicateContactPair

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface DuplicateContactPair
extends Versionable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    Represents a duplicate contact linking to both the original contact and the found duplicate contact.

      • retire

        void retire()
        Deprecated. 
        Retired this DuplicateContactPair and all its duplicate entries: 1) All the DuplicateContactPairs having the same contact and duplicate contact 2) All the DuplicateContactPairs where the contact equals this DuplicateContactPair's duplicate contact and the duplicate contact equals this DuplicateContactPair's contact.
